lead_paragraph: Steven Mendoza broke a tie in the 73rd minute and New York City FC beat the Vancouver Whitecaps 3-2 on Saturday to snap a seven-game winless streak.

headline.print_headline: Mendoza Breaks Tie in 73rd, NYC Beats Whitecaps 3-2
